data.description: Well kept home situated on Garfield Street right outside of Millville, just 40 minutes from the Jersey shore! 2 story home features 3 bedrooms and 1 bath.  1 bedroom and bath on the main floor and 2 up plus a bonus room up could be used for lots of storage, a craft room or maybe an office.  Move right in to this home with many upgrades! Exterior of home was  painted last year,  fridge about 1 year, electric panel and heater updated in 2019,  gas heat and hot water heater, fence about 1 year, main roof about 2 years, 5 AC units stay along with all appliances in their AS IS condition including washer and gas dryer.  Plus the living room tv, electric fireplace, pool and 2 sheds. Central air can be replaced by potential owner if you wish.  . Vinyl windows, and ceiling fans throughout.  Separate dining area with extra storage and counter space.  This house is a must see, schedule your showing today.
